snippet.textDisplay:
I wish I could understand every language simply to be able to listen to more music. This sounds absolutely beautiful, especially Gul Panrra's voice but reading captions isn't nearly the same as understanding the words natively. Certain words, phrases, and meanings get lost in translation so the effect of the lyrics is not as powerful as it would be understanding the song outright.

Gotta say though, even though I can't understand Gul Panrra, Atif Aslam's voice compliments hers very well in this song.
